This application is developed to enable the users to play games that are fun and also tease the brain. These games test your general knowledge and your vocabulary.

There are three modules in this application: 
1.Hangman
2.Crossword
3.Quiz

These games are quite user-friendly and require no knowledge of the coding language. But they definitely get your mind working!

More information on the games:
Hangman:The game gives a fixed number of chances to guess a word from the chosen topic. If user is  not able to do so the stick man will be hanged.
Crossword: The user will have to complete a crossword based on the topic that is chosen and he/she  will be awarded 10 points per correct answer.
Quiz: The  will have to answer 5 questions from any topic of choice and get 50 points per correct answer.
